cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this cookbook in your research or work, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "LiteRT-LM Cookbook"
abstract: >
  A collection of runnable Python scripts and Google Colab notebooks showing how to
  use LiteRT-LM to run Gemma-4 completely on-device. Covers single-turn chat,
  streaming, system prompts, GPU acceleration, speculative decoding, tool use,
  multimodal audio and vision, and a local OpenAI/Gemini-compatible API server.
